00:08:40,802 --> 00:08:42,236
but everything's fine now. So will you...

264
00:08:42,270 --> 00:08:43,771
will you, will you go
to the wedding with me?

265
00:08:43,805 --> 00:08:45,639
I-I mean, unless there's...

266
00:08:45,674 --> 00:08:46,774
there's somebody else.

267
00:08:46,808 --> 00:08:48,809
There's no one else.

268
00:08:56,375 --> 00:08:57,151
Okay.

269
00:08:57,185 --> 00:08:58,986
So, I've gathered my best boys

270
00:08:59,020 --> 00:09:00,727
to get your opinion on something.

271
00:09:01,860 --> 00:09:03,557
I'm gonna ask Mike to marry me.

272
00:09:03,591 --> 00:09:06,217
- Chang?
- What you talking 'bout, Tina?

273
00:09:06,243 --> 00:09:09,096
I got the ring and everything.

274
00:09:09,130 --> 00:09:11,665
Tina, I love you, but
this is kind of crazy.

275
00:09:11,700 --> 00:09:14,268
Is it really so crazy
for a girl to ask a boy

276
00:09:14,302 --> 00:09:15,883
for their hand in marriage these days?

277
00:09:15,909 --> 00:09:17,171
