278
00:09:17,205 --> 00:09:18,172
Yes. It is.

279
00:09:18,206 --> 00:09:19,473
I think it's romantic.

280
00:09:19,507 --> 00:09:20,724
Thank you, Blaine.

281
00:09:20,750 --> 00:09:21,758
When I was with Mike,

282
00:09:21,784 --> 00:09:23,777
I was the happiest I've ever been.

283
