the biggest mistake of my life.

286
00:09:31,619 --> 00:09:34,521
I can't afford to risk losing
him forever to some other girl.

287
00:09:34,556 --> 00:09:35,923
Grab the moment and run with it.

288
00:09:35,957 --> 00:09:37,257
ARTIE: I'm all for that,

289
00:09:37,292 --> 00:09:38,826
but how often do you guys even talk?

290
