294
00:09:45,333 --> 00:09:47,001
I can honestly say

295
00:09:47,035 --> 00:09:48,702
that Mike is my best friend again,

296
00:09:48,737 --> 00:09:50,688
and he knows me better than anyone else.

297
00:09:50,714 --> 00:09:52,139
I'd love nothing more than to see

298
00:09:52,173 --> 00:09:53,374
you and Mike together forever.

299
00:09:53,408 --> 00:09:55,643
He's awesome, you're awesome,

300
00:09:55,677 --> 00:09:57,329
and you'd be guaranteed
to have Asian kids,

301
00:09:57,355 --> 00:09:59,513
so they'd automatically be super smart.

302
00:09:59,515 --> 00:10:01,815
I'm Team Chang-Chang all the way.

303
00:10:01,817 --> 00:10:03,050
Thank you.

304
00:10:03,052 --> 00:10:04,204
What about you, Artie?

305
00:10:04,230 --> 00:10:06,186
I can't do this unless you all agree.

306
00:10:09,424 --> 00:10:11,158
I have my concerns.

307
00:10:11,192 --> 00:10:14,328
Uh, but if this is what you really want,

308
00:10:14,362 --> 00:10:16,230
then of course I support you.

309
00:10:16,829 --> 00:10:18,298
Thank you all so much.

310
00:10:18,333 --> 00:10:19,633
Yay!

311
00:10:19,668 --> 00:10:20,701
Yay.

312
00:10:20,735 --> 00:10:21,969
- Thank you, thank you.
- It's wonderful!

313
00:10:22,003 --> 00:10:23,504
PUCK: Ch-Chang!

314
00:10:24,733 --> 00:10:27,101
(school bell ringing)

315
00:10:28,804 --> 00:10:29,897
Heard you wanted to see me.

316
00:10:29,960 --> 00:10:31,635
Make it quick. I'm busy.

317
00:10:32,168 --> 00:10:33,336
Oh, okay.

318
00:10:33,370 --> 00:10:35,471
Um, well, I understand you
don't want me at your wedding

319
00:10:35,506 --> 00:10:37,507
and of course that is your prerogative,

320
00:10:37,541 --> 00:10:40,476
but for the record, I
would just like to say

321
00:10:40,511 --> 00:10:42,078
that I'm very hurt by that.

322
00:10:42,112 --> 00:10:44,447
And I fully realize that, over the years,

323
00:10:44,482 --> 00:10:47,350
uh, you and I have had a
few minor... differences.

324
00:10:47,384 --> 00:10:48,536
But weddings are the time

325
00:10:48,562 --> 00:10:50,587
