332
00:11:02,366 --> 00:11:04,334
I know how selfish and
self-centered you are.

333
00:11:04,368 --> 00:11:06,769
Like the time that you wore an exact copy

334
00:11:06,804 --> 00:11:09,172
of Emma Pillsbury's
dress to her own wedding.

335
00:11:09,206 --> 00:11:11,608
And how you perverted
the very idea of marriage

336
00:11:11,642 --> 00:11:12,775
