337
00:11:12,810 --> 00:11:15,645
You are incapable of a selfless act.

338
00:11:15,679 --> 00:11:17,906
And if you do what you
always do and just show up,

339
00:11:17,932 --> 00:11:20,216
you will be forcibly removed
by the security guards

340
00:11:20,251 --> 00:11:21,335
that I have hired.

341
00:11:22,234 --> 00:11:24,687
So have fun polishing your trophies, Sue.

342
00:11:24,722 --> 00:11:25,989
Bye.

343
00:11:34,897 --> 00:11:35,965
He's fragile, be careful.

344
00:11:36,000 --> 00:11:37,400
