356
00:12:00,357 --> 00:12:01,724
Okay.

357
00:12:01,759 --> 00:12:02,926
Um...

358
00:12:02,960 --> 00:12:03,927
(camera clicks)

359
00:12:03,961 --> 00:12:05,228
- Did you take it?
- Mm-hmm.

360
00:12:05,767 --> 00:12:07,030
I mean, everyone said it would be hard,

361
00:12:07,064 --> 00:12:08,698
but I'm telling you, man, the air force,

362
00:12:08,732 --> 00:12:09,699
it's a breeze.

363
00:12:09,733 --> 00:12:10,867
Wow, Tina.

364
00:12:10,901 --> 00:12:12,001
You look super-hot.

365
00:12:12,036 --> 00:12:13,403
Doesn't she, Mike?

366
00:12:13,437 --> 00:12:14,437
She always looks hot.

367
00:12:14,472 --> 00:12:15,281
(chuckles)

368
00:12:15,307 --> 00:12:16,940
Well, I'll, uh, leave you two.

369
00:12:18,409 --> 00:12:20,210
Oh, your tie's a little crooked.

370
00:12:20,244 --> 00:12:22,078
Just straighten that out a little bit.

371
00:12:23,758 --> 00:12:24,514
Hey, guys.

372
00:12:24,914 --> 00:12:25,748
Hey, what's up, guys?

373
00:12:25,783 --> 00:12:27,016
- Just going over my notes
- (gasps)

374
00:12:27,051 --> 00:12:28,518
before my officiating.

375
00:12:28,552 --> 00:12:30,286
Oh, you both look so
handsome in your suits.

376
00:12:30,321 --> 00:12:31,855
- BURT: Yes, you do.
- Seems like only yesterday

377
00:12:31,889 --> 00:12:33,256
