459
00:15:20,791 --> 00:15:22,726
Ew, no, Britt, no, you shouldn't do that.

460
00:15:22,760 --> 00:15:24,594
- I just felt weird about it.
- Ew.

461
00:15:26,630 --> 00:15:28,264
What the hell are you doing here?

462
00:15:30,571 --> 00:15:32,287
You know what, Britt? You
actually might be right.

463
00:15:32,313 --> 00:15:34,513
We might actually have
the worst luck of all time.

464
00:15:34,539 --> 00:15:37,494
'Cause I can't marry you if I'm
in jail for killing this bitch.

465
00:15:37,520 --> 00:15:39,288
Look, kid, I come bearing gifts.

466
00:15:39,322 --> 00:15:41,032
There's nothing that you could
give me that I would want.

467
00:15:41,058 --> 00:15:43,834
I told you I don't want
you here today, so get out.

468
00:15:43,860 --> 00:15:45,661
Well, when you see the gift I'm bearing,

469
00:15:45,695 --> 00:15:47,329
you will change your tune.

470
00:15:54,033 --> 00:15:55,467
Abuela?

471
00:15:56,668 --> 00:15:58,602
What are you doing here? What's going on?

472
00:15:58,628 --> 00:16:00,918
<i>Well, I stopped by your
abuela's house the other day,</i>

473
00:16:00,944 --> 00:16:04,110
and laid down a little reverse Sue-chology.

474
00:16:07,833 --> 00:16:09,693
Mrs. Abuela, you don't know me,

475
00:16:09,719 --> 00:16:11,516
but I coached Santana on the Cheerios!

476
00:16:11,542 --> 00:16:14,077
and worked very hard to make
sure her high school years

477
00:16:14,103 --> 00:16:15,571
were a living hell.

478
00:16:16,211 --> 00:16:18,360
For some reason, I'm not
invited to her wedding.

479
00:16:18,394 --> 00:16:19,962
And I understand that you're not going

480
00:16:19,996 --> 00:16:21,597
because of your religious beliefs.

481
00:16:21,631 --> 00:16:22,998
So I thought... who better to enlist

482
00:16:23,032 --> 00:16:24,800
to ruin her big day than you?

483
00:16:24,834 --> 00:16:26,768
So what do you think about that whole...

484
00:16:26,803 --> 00:16:29,571
stoning them to death
thing that the Bible says?

485
00:16:31,007 --> 00:16:32,474
That's horrible.

486
00:16:32,508 --> 00:16:34,376
What do you think about
having them jailed?

487
00:16:34,410 --> 00:16:36,111
Like our good friends the Russians do.

488
00:16:36,145 --> 00:16:38,680
- No!
- Okay, thinking of a more Westboro approach?

489
00:16:38,715 --> 00:16:40,515
Getting together a good
old-fashioned hate group

490
00:16:40,550 --> 00:16:41,516
and picketing?

491
00:16:41,551 --> 00:16:42,884
(scoffs)

492
00:16:45,276 --> 00:16:46,955
I was wrong.

493
00:16:47,729 --> 00:16:49,533
I'm not saying I agree

494
00:16:49,559 --> 00:16:51,526
with every decision you make.

495
00:16:51,995 --> 00:16:55,130
I still don't believe
it's right for two women

496
00:16:55,164 --> 00:16:57,866
to get married, but I do believe

497
00:16:58,510 --> 00:17:02,170
that family is the most
important thing in the world.

498
00:17:03,373 --> 00:17:05,374
And I love you, Santana.

499
00:17:07,777 --> 00:17:11,346
I don't want to be the person in
your life that causes you pain.

500
00:17:12,846 --> 00:17:15,717
And I don't want to miss the
day that I've been dreaming of

501
00:17:15,752 --> 00:17:16,885
my whole life.

502
00:17:17,713 --> 00:17:19,988
Or the birth of your kids.

503
00:17:20,023 --> 00:17:21,623
Or any other important days.

504
00:17:25,295 --> 00:17:28,297
I don't agree with everything
that you believe, either.

505
00:17:31,301 --> 00:17:32,868
<i>I just want my abuela back.</i>

506
00:17:34,518 --> 00:17:36,104
I've missed you.

507
00:17:36,139 --> 00:17:37,973
I've missed you, too.

508
00:17:41,596 --> 00:17:43,211
I always knew Sue was my good luck charm.

509
00:17:54,090 --> 00:17:55,057
Can I hug?

510
00:17:55,091 --> 00:17:56,258
SANTANA: Come on.

511
00:17:56,292 --> 00:17:57,693
- Aw...
- (laughs)

512
00:17:57,727 --> 00:17:58,694
I'm pushing it, aren't I?

513
00:17:58,728 --> 00:17:59,695
Okay, all right.

514
00:17:59,729 --> 00:18:00,829
SUE: Do your thing.

515
00:18:05,401 --> 00:18:06,768
KURT: Oh, is this so lovely.

516
00:18:06,803 --> 00:18:08,403
BLAINE: I know, it's beautiful.

517
00:18:08,438 --> 00:18:10,606
